moji\" /><br />\n淨頭幾分鐘個background，成個科幻故事設定都幾違反科學常識，再加埋成個後末世社會、教育、科技應用等，我覺得佢幾分鍾入面已經清楚表明佢硬科幻同軟科幻都垃圾<br />\n之後就係不斷比佢哋瘋狂洗腦「中國」「集體高於個人」「北京」「犧牲精神」「杭州」「高尚」「中國人拯救世界」<br />\n<br />\n呢套戲其實同啲super hero movie一樣，內容空洞低智，只有白痴fans先會話好睇然後好似護主犬咁亂吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我完全可以想像到啲大陸fans一見到批評就學啲弱智marvel撚話：「你有冇睇過原著？」「你有冇睇過佢其他系列其他書？」講一大堆廢話然後唔肯面對套戲本身係垃圾嘅事實"},{"pid":"a6703abe475175df52b636dd70b8a775810b7e70","tid":1152491,"uid":46373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b6859d974cd97e989187f8f91f3aec8700af4a7","tid":1152491,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"週經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巨怪獵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"屌 又真係幾好睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd3114bd351424bce326711e47230858623862d","tid":1152491,"uid":246256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:09:01.000Z","msg":"Designated Survivor<br />\nBillions"},{"pid":"f91ba4733d81a71398bae5786ab525b6115647e4","tid":1152491,"uid":230434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:09:52.000Z","msg":"Triple Frontier"},{"pid":"0425e15fd3aad6719e7486a825f08d2d0ce466e9","tid":1152491,"uid":34352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"Narcos"},{"pid":"408124f6cca3a910ef7978c869ce2516067a4994","tid":1152491,"uid":182600,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"又要講多次 brooklyn 99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f99d7e56cd3c98036a94110421c8781fb1940f","tid":1152491,"uid":171931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"netflix出品d戲 (電影)好多伏