" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.send小朋友之前唔訓練唔brief，等佢哋一無所知落地面送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.手環可以將生理數據send上太空，但唔允許溝通，等太空站啲人唔知地面咩事同埋比小朋友空間發揮小宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合以上問題，編劇安排獨裁者做出以上弱智決定原因只有一個：plot convenience<br />\n而編劇費盡心機放棄邏輯，就係想講班小朋友於「孤島」上同大人失去聯絡 斷絕資源 面臨危險 冇法律冇秩序 嘅情況下嘅故事，我唔肯定佢係咪想改編lord of the flies，但係兩套嘢水準差九條街喎....<br />\n大佬呀，呢套the100除咗弱智青少年仲有咩人會啱睇？"},{"pid":"76febef42db667a760e9a1458b06e4a67002ad52","tid":1152491,"uid":120987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"當然係rich and morty啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce1320f930f2eed6146b739a36f81cfaa6b6b58","tid":1152491,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JnDTmb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JnDTmb&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=3b4d046f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JnDTmb</a><br />\n原來鬼佬一早將the100同lord of the flies比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇嘅時侯都係覺得個孤島設定根本一模一樣"},{"pid":"e00e93b271439814878311a855c95e908ba25e5c","tid":1152491,"uid":210405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"非一般旅程唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf64fc74701f80cb756fa001a3acb2d1ee254d5","tid":1152491,"uid":31196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:19:31.000Z","msg":"Sherlock"},{"pid":"51de5cd6386895ec9c709a7585a1e7310ee19d92","tid":1152491,"uid":80561,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T13:23:27.000Z","msg":"安眠書店"},{"pid":"7f85f19b516157a2426f42b5567de1b38ba54473","tid":11524